    cfg.enable_stream(RS2_STREAM_DEPTH, 848, 480, RS2_FORMAT_Z16, 30);
    cfg.enable_record_to_file("camera." + std::to_string(i+1) + ".bag");

    rs2::pipeline_profile prof = pipe.start(cfg);

    i++;
}
```
However the recorded files were not synchronized: some cameras start earlier than the others; there also could be frame drops at the different timings for different cameras. 

